# InsightVerse – A Multi-Theme Blog Platform

##  Overview
InsightVerse is a blog web application built using Node.js, Express.js, and EJS.  
It allows users to create, view, edit, and delete posts across multiple themes like movies, sports, and psychology.

## 🚀 Features
- Create, edit, and delete blog posts
- View all posts on homepage
- Category-based content (Movies, Sports, Psychology)
- Responsive UI design

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express.js
- EJS
- CSS

## ⚙️ Setup
```bash
npm install
node app.js
```

## 📌 Note
This project stores data in-memory for simplicity and resets on server restart. Future versions may include database integration.

